featureType.title: Seamap Australia - WA - Seagrass Synthesis 2023 - Beaufort Inlet (2009)
featureType.abstract:
Aggregated product of all individual seagrass surveys conducted by the Department of Water (DoW), Western Australian Government, and Murdoch University Marine and Freshwater Research Laboratory (MAFR). Data was acquired by the ACEAS Seagrass Group for their 2013 Australia-wide risk assessment of Seagrass.
Subsequent data is also made available for several sites, and for additional sites, provided by the WA Department of Water and Environmental Regulation (DWER). This data synthesis is not available for download here, and users are requested to access https://data.gov.au for amore recent survey data.
